Title: Olivier, Olivier
Writer: Agnieszka Holland, Agnieszka Holland (adaptation), Yves Lapointe (adaptation), Agnieszka Holland (dialogue), Régis Debray (dialogue)
Actors: Frédéric Quiring, Faye Gatteau, Emmanuel Morozof, Brigitte Roüan
Plot: A nine-year-old boy disappears without a trace. Six years later, he reappears in Paris but there are doubts about his real identity.
